Installation instructions for FatNS
-----------------------------------

Before you start, please make sure you have the following packages installed:

* ruby1.8
* libgtk2-ruby
* libgtkhtml2-ruby
* libpcap-ruby1.8 >= 0.6-5ubuntu1 (ubuntu version is patched for findalldevs support)

Now you may run the application. Mind you, to capture, it has to be run as
root:

sudo ruby main.rb
